{"tid":1949812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指本港疫情「少少失控」   袁國勇倡病徵輕微患者轉離一線隔離病房","createTime":"2020-03-30T02:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T02:46:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aad9a84cdd31b3e231ad82f3c599e17a080337d8","tid":1949812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZKi8j9bsC3YSF5lQ6JrZ2A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200330a090403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZKi8j9bsC3YSF5lQ6JrZ2A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200330a090403.jpg&h=15e4f237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續爆發，港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇表示，本港疫情進入「少少失控」的狀態，部分病徵較輕微的患者確診後七至十日開始產生抗體，病毒量會減少，傳播風險較低，建議將病徵輕微或較年輕的患者，由一線隔離病房轉至二線隔離病房，或轉送至駿洋邨，甚至居家隔離。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇出席電台節目時表示，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3月19日前回港以及部分19日後回來的人士(湖北)，均沒有進行病毒檢測</span></span></span></strong>，加上現時病毒測試數目太少，未能識別社區病徵輕微的患者，患者追蹤亦做得很慢，無法快速切斷傳播鏈，相信有不少患者留在社區。"},{"pid":"02e1007028305d2b6c1c8095b27a13bafe321423","tid":1949812,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"邊條仆街唔肯一早封關攪到咁多唔同源頭"},{"pid":"2cdf2767882dc2fc41e88b89adfb18254ac60994","tid":1949812,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"今日下午有大量還押手足上庭跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36d354e824aafbd99890eb8e39f4520e21d6634e","tid":1949812,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:32:39.000Z","msg":"不如未開始呼吸困難都唔好去醫院，<br />\n冚家隔離囉，反正準備攬炒，<br />\n一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma